main event: A civilian reported observing one unidentified object in New Port Richey, Florida on March 17, 1969.
interesting points: The witness reported the sighting but it was not documented within the 30-day reporting window,The Air Force determined the case to be insufficient data for evaluation,The object was described as being around 30 inches in size,The witness mentioned seeing the object rise off the ground and emit a slight noise,This event is part of the historical Project Blue Book record.
